oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Martin MB-2 Bomber (NBS-1)
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Martin MB-2 Bomber at Blackwood Field in 1924. Blackwood Field was the first home of the 105th Aero Squadron stationed in Nashville. The 105th, originally named the First Squadron, Tennessee National Guard,used this field until 1927.
